# PostgreSQL :-
Why PostgreSQL?
> completely open sourse 
> complete ACID Compliance
> Comprehensive documentation and active discussions forums
> PostgreSQL is best suited for Data warehousing and data analysis applications that require fast read/write speeds.
> supported by all major cloud service providers, including Amazon, Google, & Microsoft.

To create and connect to a Database we need a SQL engine, using PostgreSQL as SQL engine.
 To write and run queries we need a graphical user interface  i.e  pgAdmin

